"Share the Invite Code with your students! Don't worry, it'll be visible "
"later on too. \n"
" \n"
" Fill out the rest of the info and click \"Create\" to create your "
"classroom."
msgstr "與您的學生分享「邀請代碼」！別擔心，稍後也會看到。\\\\n 填寫其餘的資訊，然後按一下教室。"

